ActCanadian Air Transport Security Authority Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the CATSA Aerodrome Designation Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the CATSA AERODROME DESIGNATION REGULATIONS in order to update the list of aerodromes by removing the names of airports and replacing them with the name of the city and the International Civil Aviation Organization alphanumeric location indicator, for each designated aerodrome.
